Widen an active window.

* Lisp:widen-window.el (0.1.1)
* [[http://coderepos.org/share/browser/lang/elisp/widen-window-mode/trunk/widen-window.el svn head on coderepos]]

== Features ==

* Widening an active window 

== Demo ==

http://jp.youtube.com/watch?v=cE8GZNFiM90

== Configuration ==

 (require 'widen-window)
 (global-widen-window-mode t)

----
WindowResize
CategoryWindows
